  <Risks>
    <Risk name="Overly heavy NMPC">
      <Mitigation>Build separate longitudinal and lateral NMPC controllers first; integrate only later.</Mitigation>
    </Risk>
    <Risk name="Poor plant trim">
      <Mitigation>Validate the plant and its dynamic modes before implementing the autopilot.</Mitigation>
    </Risk>
    <Risk name="No public Boeing aerodynamic data">
      <Mitigation>Use an approximate model, DATCOM/OpenVSP/OpenAP and performance calibration.</Mitigation>
    </Risk>
    <Risk name="Overly restrictive constraints">
      <Mitigation>Start with soft constraints and tighten them gradually.</Mitigation>
    </Risk>
    <Risk name="Too many modes at once">
      <Mitigation>Implement modes sequentially: ALT HOLD, SPEED HOLD, HDG SEL, LNAV, VNAV and ILS.</Mitigation>
    </Risk>
  </Risks>
